The horrific attack, which occurred on the Pelham Parkway in New York, unfolded in front of the 20-year-old's helpless new boyfriend, who watched as Espinal, knifed Katherine German in his Honda SUV.

Moments earlier, cab driver Espinal had sent the SUV driven by Jiminez, hurtling off the road and into a roll after stalking his ex-girlfriend and seeing German leave a Bronx hotel with her new boyfriend at 4 a.m. on Wednesday morning.

